description: For sale: $229,000. Exceptional 3 season Birch Lake cabin for a couple or family. This +- .93 acre USFS lease lot in the South Birch Lake summer Home Group is one of the most wooded lots with huge 80' red and white pines, and has almost 200 feet of shoreline with beautiful views to north. The main cabin has living room with wood burning freestanding stove, kitchen, dining area, two bedrooms (sleeps 4) and bath. The main cabin also has air conditioning. The detached outbuilding (14 x 30) has one large (10 x 13) office/rec room, bathroom, laundry area, shop area (8 x 12) and two enclosed lean-tos for yard appliances and misc. storage. The cabin and outbuilding have both been architecturally upgraded with Marvin windows, Cambria quartz countertops, plumbing and electrical, wood flooring, cedar T & G ceilings, all new appliances including washer/dryer. New roofing on both buildings in 2008. This property comes semi-furnished with all beds, kitchen table and chairs, 2 recliners and desk. The lake water system has a Seagull water purifier for drinking. There are separate 20 gallon electric water heaters in each building. Both buildings are insulated and have base board electric heat. The main cabin has fiber optic high speed internet and Wi-Fi.  Also included is the 28 foot aluminum dock.  Fantastic property in a great location for $229,000.  NO SHOWINGS UNTIL MAY 1, 2020

Lower level is finished out with a rec room and a den that is currently used as another bedroom (non-egress) and a 3/4 bath.  Large utility room.  Home also features a newer architectural shingle roof, updated windows and fresh paint inside and out.

description: For sale: $695,000. Year round living at waters edge on beautiful Bear Island Lake. This property holds a phenomenal WESTERLY view with +-155' of sand beach and nestles on +-3.4 acres. The home was built in 2002 hosting 3 bedrooms and 3 baths. Exceptional gourmet kitchen with native rock, maple custom cabinetry, mountain alder floor, working island with cook top/exhaust fan, and double ovens. The kitchen opens up to dining and living area and extends into a beautiful enclosed 4 season room and then onto an open deck system all facing the water. The home features a large master bedroom with walk in closet and master bath with jacuzzi tub and atrium doors leading you onto the deck facing the lake. Also, sauna, main floor laundry, storage area and 2 huge work rooms that could be converted into more living space, free standing soap stone fireplace in walkout and 2nd free standing fireplace in the 4 season room. This home has what we call a Bird's Nest!!! This room features custom cabinets and bookshelves and a perfect sitting area for the most expansive view of Bear Island Lake. There is even more with attached 3 stall insulated garage, renovated boat house and additional 1 car garage and shed.

description: Recently sold: $147,000. Unique country property on 6.3+/- acres with mature tree cover, open areas with garden beds, walking paths and slight view of Birch Lake River. Recently sold: $165,000. 100 feet of sand beach fronts this immaculate home. Beautiful garden plots and storage buildings compliment the yard. Updated in 2003 brought new vinyl siding with soffits, all new windows, complete interior remodel, new furnace and electrical service. The large 9 x 12 foyer with closet opens to the large lakeside living room with stonework woodburning fireplace. The kitchen, dining room and living room are a wall of windows that overlook beautiful Birch Lake. The master bedroom features large walk-in closets and an attached full bath. The full walkout basement with large recreation room, second bedroom, laundry, storage and utility plus a 3/4 bath is tastefully done and expands the living area and privacy for guests. Plenty of well maintained yard space for outside social gatherings to include a large wraparound deck. The lower level boasts a spacious tv/living room with a second gas fireplace, a walkout to the lake and the third bedroom and third bathroom. Plenty of storage space along with a bonus room that may used as an office or sewing room. Oversized attached two car garage, storage shed and of course the detached wood burning finnish style sauna located closer to the lake. description: For sale: $169,900. Sprawling 5 bedroom, 4 bathroom home with a 3 car detached garage on a corner lot! Walk into the home and see the newly rebuilt apartment with 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom, and an unfinished kitchen that is waiting for you to add your choice of cabinets, cupboards and appliances. This apartment has in-floor heating housed in a concrete floor hat has been painted with decorative epoxy paint. Next walk through the office to get to the newly carpeted upper level with three freshly painted spacious bedrooms and a brand-new rebuilt bathroom- new shower/tub, new toilet, new sink, new walls. Walk down the steps to enjoy meticulously cared for hard wood floors decorating the master bedroom, the main level living room and the dining room. Snuggle up to the propane fireplace on those cold winter nights. The kitchen just received a new linoleum floor. The basement has a decorative fireplace in the living area, a utilities room, a storage room, washer dryer hook ups and another 3/4 bathroom with a new sink. There is a windowed 3 season patio attached to the back of the detached 3 stall garage. This home is only 1 block away from biking, hiking and a.t.v. trails. If you need a spacious home to live in, this home is a must see!
